  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌙 <strong>Night Market Simulator: Build and Grow Your Own Night Market!</strong> 🌙</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready for a real night market experience?</strong><br><strong>Night Market Simulator</strong> is a detailed and fun simulation game where you build and expand your own market, make strategic decisions while buying and selling products.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open your store, stock the shelves, meet customer needs, unlock new products with licenses, and grow your business by managing your employees!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/3b9a5dc3af2bc5ef999a0d371ced4a5a.poster.avif?t=1746377671\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/3b9a5dc3af2bc5ef999a0d371ced4a5a.webm?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/3b9a5dc3af2bc5ef999a0d371ced4a5a.mp4?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📘 <strong>About the Game</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Night Market Simulator</strong> offers players the chance to build, manage, and grow their own night market in a deep trading simulation.<br>In a buy-and-sell system, price your products strategically, meet customer demands, and grow your business!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪ <strong>License System:</strong><br>Sell products, level up, and unlock new product licenses. Each license means more items and more profit!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/b9dbde839a3994e0378e6ee45bb10fda.poster.avif?t=1746377671\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/b9dbde839a3994e0378e6ee45bb10fda.webm?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/b9dbde839a3994e0378e6ee45bb10fda.mp4?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪ <strong>Warehouse and Stock Management:</strong><br>Receive products in boxes, transfer them to storage, stock up, and create an organized system by filling your shelves.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/44996e835d01ebcc64aaa1b83d4403d9.poster.avif?t=1746377671\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/44996e835d01ebcc64aaa1b83d4403d9.webm?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/44996e835d01ebcc64aaa1b83d4403d9.mp4?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪ <strong>Employee Management:</strong><br>Hire workers like cashiers, stock movers, and shelf organizers. Increase automation and use your time efficiently!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/1aff5627baf11bc3b91a2713c364e3cd.poster.avif?t=1746377671\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/1aff5627baf11bc3b91a2713c364e3cd.webm?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/1aff5627baf11bc3b91a2713c364e3cd.mp4?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪ <strong>Expandable Store:</strong><br>Use your earnings to expand your store, unlock new areas, and showcase more products. Bigger space means more customers!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/73a042aecc3dd0033f275f5552bf4ab4.poster.avif?t=1746377671\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/73a042aecc3dd0033f275f5552bf4ab4.webm?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/73a042aecc3dd0033f275f5552bf4ab4.mp4?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪ <strong>Different Shelf Categories:</strong><br>Set up your store with various product placement types like freezers, refrigerators, shelves, and fruit stands.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/94ed513a357289f205ca1f7af7a96b20.poster.avif?t=1746377671\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/94ed513a357289f205ca1f7af7a96b20.webm?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/94ed513a357289f205ca1f7af7a96b20.mp4?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪ <strong>Dynamic Pricing and Profit-Loss Calculation:</strong><br>Set your own product prices, adjust profit margins, and optimize your business with smart trading strategies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/eb464cdf5398194c5bb4666b82fa9506.poster.avif?t=1746377671\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/eb464cdf5398194c5bb4666b82fa9506.webm?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/eb464cdf5398194c5bb4666b82fa9506.mp4?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪ <strong>Store Customization:</strong><br>Give your store a name, personalize its look, and reflect your unique style!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/52a9192124521dda43cf125301d0d557.poster.avif?t=1746377671\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/52a9192124521dda43cf125301d0d557.webm?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109210/extras/52a9192124521dda43cf125301d0d557.mp4?t=1746377671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 <strong>Game Modes and Content</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪ <strong>Free Play:</strong><br>Play at your own pace and develop your business however you want.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪ <strong>Missions and Objectives:</strong><br>Complete specific tasks to earn rewards and progress through guided goals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤝 <strong>Community and Development Process</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Night Market Simulator</strong> is a game shaped by community feedback.<br>Each update brings new content, improvements, and additions based on player suggestions.<br><strong>Your ideas matter to us!</strong></p>",
